" INFO:
" [count]<leader>cX
" cc	comment
" cn	comment, forced nesting
" cu	uncomment
" c<space>	toggle
" ci	invert
" cy	yanking + commenting
" c$	comment from the cursor to the end of line
" cA	add comment to the end of line and go to insert mode
" c{l,b}	aligned left/right

